    {
      "name": "Tracking Shot",
      "slot": "secondary fire",
      "type": "Ability",
      "shot_type": [
        "[[File:Ability-dva7.png|40x40px|sub|class=inline-icon invert-image|link=Projectile|Projectile ]] Projectile"
      ],
      "raw": {
        "hero name": "Sierra",
        "ability name": "Tracking Shot",
        "ability key": "secondary fire",
        "ability type": "Ability",
        "shot type": "[[File:Ability-dva7.png|40x40px|sub|class=inline-icon invert-image|link=Projectile|Projectile ]] <span class=\"tooltip\" title=\"Has travel time.\">Projectile</span>",
        "official description": "Marks an enemy. Helix Rifle shots automatically track marked enemies.",
        "damage": "35",
        "damage falloff range": "",
        "headshot": "yes",
        "headshot mod": "2",
        "heal": "",
        "cooldown": "10 seconds",
        "charges": "",
        "fire rate": "",
        "ammo": "",
        "reload time": "",
        "cast time": "<span class=\"tooltip\" title=\"0.288s startup + 0.412s recovery\">0.3 + 0.4 seconds</span>",
        "duration": "3 seconds (tracking)",
        "pspeed": "140 m/s",
        "pradius": "0.26 meters",
        "spread": "",
        "radius": "",
        "range distance": "",
        "dps": "",
        "hps": "",
        "ability keywords": "critical::lesser reloads::travel time::sticky",
        "ability details": "* After a successful hit on an enemy, <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Helix Rifle\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Helix Rifle.png|sub|link=Sierra#Helix Rifle|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Sierra#Helix Rifle|Helix Rifle]]</span> is automatically reloaded and its spread is automatically reduced to its minimum value for Tracking Shot's duration while the tracked enemy is within Line of Sight.\n* Can be reactivated to remove the mark.\n* The initial projectile can be critically hit, however any tracking shots cannot.\n* While an enemy is marked:\n** All shots fired from <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Helix Rifle\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Helix Rifle.png|sub|link=Sierra#Helix Rifle|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Sierra#Helix Rifle|Helix Rifle]]</span> whilst the mark is in Line of Sight will fire towards them, as long as you are aiming within approximately 90 degrees of the target.\n** Any tracking shots will not use ammo.\n** A visual UI mark will be on the target, visible even behind cover.\n*** This becomes red and smaller when the target is in Line of Sight, whilst white and larger if they're behind cover.\n* The initial marking projectile can be deflected with <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Deflect\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability-genji2.png|sub|link=Genji#Deflect|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Genji#Deflect|Deflect]]</span>, but the auto-aim properties will not apply.\n* The projectile is Sticky and functions similarly to <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Jagged Blade\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Jagged_Blade_Icon.png|sub|link=Junker Queen#Jagged Blade|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Junker Queen#Jagged Blade|Jagged Blade]]</span> or <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Pulse Bomb\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability-tracer4.png|sub|link=Tracer#Pulse Bomb|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Tracer#Pulse Bomb|Pulse Bomb]]</span>.\n** Phasing abilities, such as <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Swift Step\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Swift_Step_Icon.png|sub|link=Kiriko#Swift Step|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Kiriko#Swift Step|Swift Step]]</span> or <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Wraith Form\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability-reaper2.png|sub|link=Reaper#Wraith Form|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Reaper#Wraith Form|Wraith Form]]</span> will remove the mark.\n** Cleansing abilities (that do not Phase), such as <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Projected Barrier\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability-zarya3.png|sub|link=Zarya#Projected Barrier|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Zarya#Projected Barrier|Projected Barrier]]</span> or <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Life Grip\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Life_Grip_Icon.png|sub|link=Lifeweaver#Life Grip|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Lifeweaver#Life Grip|Life Grip]]</span>, will not remove the mark."
      },
