        "ability keywords": "fixed::ignore barrier;;deployable::deployable;;invulnerable::travel time;;deployable",
        "ability details": "* The bombs are deployed from an indestructible drone, that will spread them out in 8 rows of 3, with the final row having only 2.\n* During deployment, the bombs are considered standard projectiles and can be blocked by [[barriers]] or negated by abilities such as <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Defense Matrix\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability-dva3.png|sub|link=D.Va#Defense Matrix|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[D.Va#Defense Matrix|Defense Matrix]]</span> or <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"Kinetic Grasp\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Abilities-sigma3.png|sub|link=Sigma#Kinetic Grasp|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Sigma#Kinetic Grasp|Kinetic Grasp]]</span>.\n** Once they hit a surface, the bombs are primed and explode after a 1 second delay.\n* The drone will travel a minimum of ~2m height above the ground, regardless of the angle deployed.\n* The drone will always travel diagonally if the player angles it too far up or down.\n* Both the drone and the projectiles can be destroyed with <span class=\"ability-tooltip\" data-ability=\"EMP\" ><span class=\"ability-link\">[[File:Ability Sombra EMP.png|sub|link=Sombra#EMP|40x40px |class=inline-icon invert-image]]</span>&#32;[[Sombra#EMP|EMP]]</span> prior to detonating, regardless of whether the projectiles are in motion or on a surface."
